          <td class="NewsText" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">On this day, we shall come together with our allies in the JusticeBringers in an attempt to OWN this zone. <br><br>This raid is focused at our 35-45 members, but anyone 31 and up may join.<br><br>We are not raiding for any particular items, although there are a few that are nice things that drop (Robe of Foci, Robe of Dalnir, Two Hand Practice Sword, and a TON of Monk items). We are going share pure fun and excitement with our allies.<br><br>Getting to the zone can be tricky, and I urge you all to print maps or find a partner to travel with. The entrance to the zone can be found at approximately pos 3500 by pos 4000 in the Warsliks Woods area of Kunark. I will help guide and port as much as possible, but since I am organizing the raid I cannot guarantee my availability. We shall plan to meet in the caverns where the zoneline is located at Noon EST (18:00 CET).<br><br>I will assign groupleaders that will be the master looters for each group. They will also relay communication to and from me, so please follow any instructions they may give.<br><br>As for valuable loot, the rules are as follows: All those that can use the item get first dibs by way of rolls by me or other designated event leaders (to be anounced day of). If there is no one that can use an particular drop, it will then be made available to all by way of a random roll of those that show interest. <br><br>I hate to be strict, but failure to abide by any of these rules could result in immediate disbandment from your group and possibly the loss of ability to participate in future raids.<br><br>Lets show them what we are made of!!<br><br>Thalador - The Surnameless<br><br>"Courage is not the absence of fear, but the judgment that there is something more important than fear."<br><br>
